org.eclipse.scada.vi.details.model.impl

Class ReadableComponentImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • EObjectImpl
      • org.eclipse.scada.vi.details.model.impl.ComponentImpl
        • org.eclipse.scada.vi.details.model.impl.ReadableComponentImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Component, ReadableComponent
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ProgressComponentImpl, TextComponentImpl, ValueComponentImpl, WriteableComponentImpl

    public abstract class ReadableComponentImpl
extends ComponentImpl
implements ReadableComponent
    An implementation of the model object 'Readable Component'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Format
    • Decimal
    • Attribute
    • Hd Connection Id
    • Hd Item Id
    • Hd Query String
    • Is Text
